text: Dolphin Tale 2 is a 2014 American family movie written and directed by Charles Martin Smith. It is the sequel to his 2011 movie Dolphin Tale. The movie stars Harry Connick Jr., Ashley Judd, Nathan Gamble, Cozi Zuehlsdorff, Kris Kristofferson, Morgan Freeman, Juliana Harkavy, Austin Stowell, Betsy Landin, Austin Highsmith and Tom Nowicki with Bethany Hamilton. It was released on September 12, 2014. ==References== Category:2014 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:American family movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies about whales Category:Movies set in Florida Category:Movies set underwater
